responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "05E7893E43052BB6E932C2AE3DF74ABA", "Bloom is too big now. Its blight will consume. But brothers give me clue before they bleed. Master Alo says a potion, a killer of blooms! Can be made and tossed upon the great Blight Bloom/ Ends the curse it will. I can make such a potion, but I must know the parts for the whole.")
